To run this code, you will need two free API keys.

1. Google Gemini API Key (For the Brain/Scripting)
Go to Google AI Studio.

Sign in with your Google account.

Click on "Get API key" in the left-hand menu.

Click "Create API key" and copy the generated string.

Paste this key into the GEMINI_API_KEY variable in the script.

2. Hugging Face Access Token (For Image Generation)
Go to Hugging Face and create a free account.

Click on your profile picture in the top right and go to Settings.

Select Access Tokens from the left menu.

Click "New token" (a 'Read' role is fine for this).

Copy the generated token and paste it into the HUGGINGFACE_TOKEN variable in the script.
